#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.deg2rad.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.deg2rad"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:1 of
msgid "Convert angles from degrees to radians."
msgstr "将角度从度数转换为弧度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:3 of
msgid "Angles in degrees."
msgstr "以度为单位的角度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:15 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding angle in radians."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的弧度角。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rad2deg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:21 of
msgid "Convert angles from radians to degrees."
msgstr "将角度从弧度转换为度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`unwrap`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:24 of
msgid "Remove large jumps in angle by wrapping."
msgstr "通过包裹方式移除角度中的大跳跃。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.deg2rad.deg2rad:28 of
msgid "``deg2rad(x)`` is ``x * pi / 180``."
msgstr "``deg2rad(x)`` 等价于 ``x * pi / 180``。"

